01:54.080 --> 01:57.232
Ehh, death by natural causes.

02:01.200 --> 02:04.796
Natural causes, natural causes.

02:05.440 --> 02:07.796
More natural causes.
I hate natural causes!

02:07.800 --> 02:10.952
Give me a big old stab wound
to poke around in, then I'm happy.

02:10.960 --> 02:13.634
Ahh, here we are.

02:13.640 --> 02:15.074
Body bags.

02:15.080 --> 02:17.720
See, if it's murder or suicide
or a nasty accident,

02:17.720 --> 02:19.757
they put 'em in these bags.

02:19.760 --> 02:22.400
This one was found
on a stretch of lonely highway,

02:22.400 --> 02:25.677
miles from the nearest town
on a pitch-black night.

02:33.720 --> 02:38.397
<i>Also in the news, another gruesome
murder in Haddonfield today.</i>

02:38.400 --> 02:40.915
<i>The body of a young woman
was discovered buried</i>

02:40.920 --> 02:43.310
<i>in the bottom of a trash bin
behind a shopping mall.</i>

02:43.320 --> 02:47.109
<i>Police Chief, Ardith Robinson
of the Haddonfield PD</i>

02:47.120 --> 02:49.760
<i>gave a statement
