<i>another victim of a serial killer
responsible for a series</i>

02:58.440 --> 03:01.035
<i>of ritualized slayings
in the southland.</i>

03:01.040 --> 03:02.952
<i>The body of the woman
was found by hikers--</i>

03:02.960 --> 03:06.556
I'd be scared shitless working
all alone in a place like this.

03:06.560 --> 03:08.597
Eh, I can take care of myself.

03:08.600 --> 03:11.957
Besides, you're the one who has
to drive back to an empty apartment.

03:11.960 --> 03:14.156
- Ooooh.
- Thanks a lot.

03:14.160 --> 03:16.231
You don't mind
picking me up in the morning?

03:16.240 --> 03:17.958
<i>- What time?
- Seven.</i>

03:17.960 --> 03:18.996
Ooh.

03:19.000 --> 03:21.117
This'll be the last time
I ask you for a ride, I promise.

03:21.120 --> 03:23.316
They said my car will be
out of the shop by tomorrow.

03:23.320 --> 03:25.437
I'll buy breakfast.

03:26.680 --> 03:27.716
Deal.

03:27.720 --> 03:29.234
See ya.

03:39.480 --> 03:41.312
<i>Can I help ya?</i>

03:41.320 --> 03:42.959
I'm Anne.

03:42.960 --> 03:44.075
Okay.

03:44.080 --> 03:46.117
The new girl.

03:46.120 --> 03:48.157
Oh, yeah, right,
come on in.

03:55.120 --> 03:56.349
- Hi.
- Hey.

03:56.360 --> 03:58.317
- Sorry I'm late.
- No biggie.

03:58.320 --> 04:01.233
Oh, wow, this is almost identical
to the gas station I worked last month,

04:01.240 --> 04:02.754
except that was a little bit smaller.

04:02.760 --> 04:05.229
Well, why don't I give you
the, uh, the grand tour.

04:05.240 --> 04:07.880
Uh, that's the cash register.

04:07.880 --> 04:09.678
You just punch in the pump number
and amount, right?

04:09.680 --> 04:11.194
Yeah, you got it.
That's the credit card machine.

04:11.200 --> 04:12.236
No sweat.

04:12.240 --> 04:13.469
And listen, when you get
their, uh, signatures,

04:13.480 --> 04:15.119
