plate number, all right?

04:15.120 --> 04:16.394
- Right.
- It's important.

04:16.399 --> 04:18.959
Um, the TV gets
maybe three channels.

04:18.959 --> 04:20.872
Actually, I'll probably just
do some studying.

04:20.880 --> 04:23.520
