04:24.680 --> 04:25.875
Is that the bathroom?

04:25.880 --> 04:29.271
Well, actually, we, uh, prefer
to call that the employee's lounge.

04:29.280 --> 04:30.759
Yeah, great.

04:30.760 --> 04:32.672
Let's see-- oh, oh,
do I ring out the register

04:32.680 --> 04:34.194
