comes in?

04:34.200 --> 04:37.033
Nah, just, you know,
uh, he'll take care of that.

04:37.040 --> 04:39.635
Why don't you just collect
the cash and make change.

04:39.640 --> 04:41.791
- Okay.
- Yep-- oh, you know what?

04:41.800 --> 04:43.837
This door locks automatically
if you leave the booth.

04:43.840 --> 04:45.160
- So, uh--
- Keys?

04:45.160 --> 04:46.639
Right, keys, yeah, um--

04:46.640 --> 04:49.109
God, I don't know
where the hell I left them.

04:49.120 --> 04:50.679
Yeah, here they are.

04:50.680 --> 04:53.070
The round one,
um, that's for the booth

04:53.080 --> 04:54.719
and the square one
works everything else, okay?

04:54.720 --> 04:55.915
Got it.

04:55.920 --> 04:58.150
- Public restrooms.
- Yeah.

04:59.160 --> 05:03.154
Um... yeah, I guess
that's about it.

05:04.400 --> 05:06.915
You know, I feel a little bit guilty.

05:06.920 --> 05:08.752
Leaving you out here
all by yourself.

05:08.760 --> 05:10.797
- Eh, I'll be okay.
- Did you hear the news tonight?

05:10.800 --> 05:12.393
<i>- Yeah, it's horrible.
- Yeah.</i>

05:12.400 --> 05:14.039
- Hmm.
- Hey, you know what?

05:14.040 --> 05:15.997
If you got a problem,

05:16.000 --> 05:19.550
why don't you,
um, just give me a call, okay?

05:19.560 --> 05:20.710
<i>Hey, thank you.</i>

05:20.720 --> 05:21.870
<i>- Sure, no problem.
- Will do.</i>

05:21.880 --> 05:23.155
Okay.

05:23.160 --> 05:24.799
Uh, that's it, then.

05:25.360 --> 05:26.874
I'm outta here.
Have a good night.

05:26.880 --> 05:28.792
- See ya later.
- You got it.

06:40.040 --> 06:41.235
Pack of Coronados.

06:44.520 --> 06:46.238
Two seventy-five.

07:16.680 --> 07:17.795
Ls there anything else?

07:19.160 --> 07:21.277
