to college myself, you know?

07:34.160 --> 07:36.038
Yeah, I got some bourbon
out in the car.

07:36.040 --> 07:38.396
Maybe I can get you
to come out of that booth.

07:44.720 --> 07:46.632
Maybe I'll see ya around.

08:18.120 --> 08:19.713
Okay.

08:31.400 --> 08:33.039
Okay.

08:59.680 --> 09:02.513
Hi, I need to fill her up.
Super unleaded.

09:03.120 --> 09:05.157
- Number 12?
- Uh, yeah.

09:53.640 --> 09:55.040
Haven't seen you
around here before.

09:55.040 --> 09:58.033
It's my first night-- huh.

09:58.040 --> 10:00.509
<i>Uh, signature
and license, please.</i>

10:02.200 --> 10:03.839
Are you from Haddonfield?

10:04.600 --> 10:06.114
Born and raised.

10:10.680 --> 10:12.114
Thanks.

10:12.120 --> 10:13.156
<i>What are you studying?</i>

10:13.360 --> 10:16.319
Um, psychology.
Final exams next week.

10:16.320 --> 10:17.959
<i>Gotta pull my average up.</i>

10:17.960 --> 10:20.680
- You go to the university?
- Uh-huh.

10:20.680 --> 10:22.512
Well, do you ever feel like,
uh, kicking back?

10:22.520 --> 10:24.318
You know, just hanging out
someplace after class?

10:25.440 --> 10:27.591
<i>- Sometimes.
- Well, you gotta try the Oak Lounge.</i>

10:27.600 --> 10:29.717
<i>It's, uh, down Seventh Street
by the freeway.</i>

10:29.720 --> 10:32.599
They got a really good band there
on weekends.

10:32.600 --> 10:36.992
Hey, maybe if I run into you some time,
I'll play you a game of pool.

10:37.000 --> 10:38.354
I'm no good at pool.

10:38.360 --> 10:39.396
All the better.

10:40.440 --> 10:42.955
Well, see ya.

10:44.400 --> 10:45.356
Bye.

11:07.680 --> 11:08.875
Ooh.

11:10.000 --> 11:13.675
Hey, you forgot your card!
Hey!

11:28.920 --> 11:30.274
Shit.

12:00.720 --> 12:02.632
Ooh!
Great.

12:17.080 --> 12:18.195
<i>Hey.</i>

12:18.200 --> 12:20.317
I need the key to the restroom.

12:23.520 --> 12:25.637
I really have to go
to the restroom.

12:25.640 --> 12:29.031
Oh, uh... the key's in the booth.

12:29.720 --> 12:31.040
<i>I have to get the other set.</i>

12:31.040 --> 12:32.758
Uh, I'll be right back.

12:55.280 --> 12:56.600
Shit.

13:09.360 --> 13:10.919
Ugh, thank God!

13:32.280 --> 13:33.919
Great.

14:41.760 --> 14:43.478
Oh, you pump,
I gotta go to the john.

14:43.480 --> 14:44.675
I'm gonna take care of this.

14:44.680 --> 14:47.559
Whoo-hoo, honey,
hiya, sweetheart!

14:47.560 --> 14:50.314
Listen, give me,
uh, oh, $20.

14:50.320 --> 14:52.152
Of that
superduper irregular

14:52.160 --> 14:55.631
on, uh, pump number
niner there, okay?

14:57.080 --> 14:59.356
You're a little glum tonight, hon,
what's wrong?

14:59.360 --> 15:00.839
You oughtta be out partyin'.

15:00.840 --> 15:02.752
<i>Pretty little thing
like you, huh?</i>

15:04.480 --> 15:08.440
Say, uh, I need a key to get
in that little boy's room there?

15:08.440 --> 15:09.874
Uh, you do.

15:09.880 --> 15:11.394
Listen, could you do me a favor?

15:12.240 --> 15:13.754
Sure, name it.

15:13.760 --> 15:16.150
There's a man,
he's in the men's restroom.

15:16.160 --> 15:18.390
- He's a little weird.
- Weirdo, huh?

15:18.400 --> 15:20.153
Yeah, I don't know--
I was wondering,

15:20.160 --> 15:21.753
could you take a look
and see what he's doing?

15:23.000 --> 15:24.354
You got that.

15:30.640 --> 15:33.633
Yoo-hoo!
There's nothing coming out.

15:38.040 --> 15:39.110
What's the problem?

15:39.120 --> 15:41.510
Oh, oh, there's nothing
coming out.

15:41.520 --> 15:44.752
<i>- You have to lift the lever.
- Oh.</i>

15:44.760 --> 15:47.195
No. The lever--
the lever on the pump.

15:48.440 --> 15:50.193
Never mind, I'll do it.

16:00.720 --> 16:02.199
<i>So sorry to bother you.</i>

16:02.200 --> 16:04.317
I just usually go
to the full serve.

16:05.600 --> 16:07.079
Oh.

16:07.080 --> 16:09.720
Oh, thanks.

16:13.240 --> 16:14.515
Guy is sleepin' in there.

16:14.520 --> 16:16.113
He's all curled up
around the toilet.

16:16.120 --> 16:18.919
I had to stand back
and aim over his head.

16:18.920 --> 16:20.911
Shame on you.

16:20.920 --> 16:23.196
When you gotta go,
you gotta go.

16:24.440 --> 16:25.999
I wouldn't worry about it, hon.

16:26.000 --> 16:27.878
He's fast asleep.
The guy's a bum.

16:27.880 --> 16:29.155
Let him sleep it off.

16:29.160 --> 16:30.435
Did you get the restroom key?

16:30.440 --> 16:32.397
Oh, I left it hangin'
in the door.

16:32.400 --> 16:35.040
Come on, baby, let's go,
I'm cold.

16:35.040 --> 16:36.872
See ya around, doll face.

16:36.880 --> 16:38.633
Get in there, get in there,
arrrh!

17:54.920 --> 17:56.274
God.

18:38.440 --> 18:40.318
<i>Shit!</i>

18:46.800 --> 18:48.029
I can do this.

20:28.080 --> 20:31.471
Come on, come on...

20:39.040 --> 20:40.235
Hi.

20:41.880 --> 20:43.200
This is Bill.

20:44.960 --> 20:47.316
I can't come
to the phone right now.

20:48.120 --> 20:50.715
So, maybe you could
just leave a message.

20:50.720 --> 20:53.280
See, I got a sore throat.

20:53.280 --> 20:56.113
<i>Be better if you could
call back.</i>

20:56.120 --> 20:59.716
If you wanna leave a message,
just wait for the beep.

20:59.720 --> 21:00.995
<i>Beep.</i>

21:27.840 --> 21:29.240
Come on, come on, come on.

21:31.280 --> 21:32.714
Come on!

21:35.400 --> 21:37.312
Answer the phone!

21:40.800 --> 21:43.315
- 9-1-1--
- Oh, there's a man!

21:43.320 --> 21:45.880
He's after me!
He's after me!

23:59.600 --> 24:01.079
Bitch.

25:49.600 --> 25:50.954
Oh!

26:00.000 --> 26:02.674
Die, you son of a bitch!

26:24.960 --> 26:26.474
Forgot my credit card.

26:44.080 --> 26:46.675
Tell me, how long have you had
these feelings of hostility?

26:47.560 --> 26:48.755
You can't say?

26:48.760 --> 26:52.435
You know, you really shouldn't keep
your emotions all bottled up inside.

26:54.560 --> 26:56.631
Eh, you're hopeless!

26:56.640 --> 26:58.040
He should have had a lobotomy.

26:58.960 --> 27:01.759
Let's go see what other fun things
we can find to do.

27:06.080 --> 27:08.276
Cirrhosis of the liver.

27:08.280 --> 27:09.634
Brain tumor.

27:11.200 --> 27:12.634
Severe head cold?

27:12.640 --> 27:15.030
Let's check the drawers.

27:15.040 --> 27:17.635
I call these
my necrophile cabinets.

27:22.360 --> 27:24.317
Seems to be stuck.

27:28.920 --> 27:30.399
Obviously,
these drawers were built

27:30.400 --> 27:33.313
before breast implants
became so popular.

27:33.320 --> 27:34.754
These oughtta be recycled.

27:40.480 --> 27:41.994
That's odd.

27:46.360 --> 27:47.635
Ooh.

27:47.640 --> 27:49.154
Marital spat?

27:52.800 --> 27:54.200
Kiss and make up.

27:57.480 --> 27:59.278
Ahh.

28:02.800 --> 28:05.554
Believe it or not,
this was a human body.

28:05.560 --> 28:09.031
Poor guy fell off a high-rise
onto the top of a car,

28:09.040 --> 28:10.838
which swerved in front
of a train

28:10.840 --> 28:13.753
and was dragged 900 yards
under the engine.

28:13.760 --> 28:16.150
Fascinating what can happen
to the human body

28:16.160 --> 28:17.674
under the right circumstances.

