<i>Light winds,
lows in the upper 50s.</i>

28:38.160 --> 28:40.595
<i>High tomorrow
in the mid 70s.</i>

28:40.600 --> 28:42.114
<i>And now this--</i>

28:42.120 --> 28:44.476
<i>At the Roswell Hair Growth
Laboratories,</i>

28:44.480 --> 28:47.359
<i>we have perfected
a simple surgical procedure</i>

28:47.360 --> 28:51.559
<i>to restore full hair growth
virtually overnight.</i>

28:51.560 --> 28:54.280
<i>After my Roswell Hair
growth treatment,</i>

28:55.360 --> 28:57.113
<i>I bought the company.</i>

29:13.080 --> 29:14.833
<i>- Hi.
- Hi.</i>

29:17.080 --> 29:18.275
What's wrong?

29:19.080 --> 29:20.230
Nothing.

29:21.280 --> 29:22.475
Come on in.

29:31.240 --> 29:32.390
More wine?

29:32.400 --> 29:34.118
Mm, I'd love some.

29:43.480 --> 29:45.198
- Richard?
- Hm?

29:45.200 --> 29:46.190
What did you do to your hair?

29:48.960 --> 29:50.110
Nothing.

29:51.720 --> 29:54.155
Well, I mean,
I combed it a different way.

29:54.160 --> 29:56.880
Sweetheart, are you worried
about your hair thinning?

29:56.880 --> 29:59.270
No, of course not.

29:59.280 --> 30:02.239
I think you look
very distinguished.

30:02.240 --> 30:03.799
You're very handsome.

30:07.960 --> 30:09.189
You don't like it, do you?

30:09.200 --> 30:11.191
I like you.

30:12.080 --> 30:13.400
<i>Eat.</i>

30:18.000 --> 30:19.514
This veal is delicious, you know.

30:21.200 --> 30:24.159
So, you think I'm going bald?

30:24.160 --> 30:25.753
No, I don't.

30:27.240 --> 30:28.993
What's the big deal,
if you are anyway?

30:29.000 --> 30:30.753
Oh, so, now I am going bald?

30:30.760 --> 30:32.990
It really doesn't matter to me.

30:33.000 --> 30:35.435
Are you telling me
that you don't like hair?

30:35.440 --> 30:37.158
Of course, I like hair.

30:37.160 --> 30:38.753
Then how can you stand
looking at me?

30:39.920 --> 30:41.274
I mean, look at this.

30:41.280 --> 30:42.600
Look at that, huh?

30:42.600 --> 30:46.275
Richard,
you're behaving like a baby.

30:46.280 --> 30:48.431
Well, why not?
I got hair like a baby.

31:07.600 --> 31:09.159
Why don't you let me make
an appointment

31:09.160 --> 31:10.833
for you with my hairdresser?

31:10.840 --> 31:13.036
Dennis'll give your hair
a nice shape.

31:13.040 --> 31:14.758
I don't need shape.

31:14.760 --> 31:16.877
I need quantity.
I need volume.

31:16.880 --> 31:18.359
I need more hair.

31:18.360 --> 31:19.794
Now, what about this?

31:21.320 --> 31:23.118
- Huh?
- Forget it!

31:23.120 --> 31:24.998
- No way, no way!
- Wait, wait, wait, hey, hey!

31:25.000 --> 31:27.117
Come on,
just give it a chance.

31:27.120 --> 31:28.395
Take a look at it!

31:30.640 --> 31:32.950
- You mean--
- That looks ridiculous.

31:32.960 --> 31:35.316
- It won't fool anybody.
- Would you be careful with that?

31:40.680 --> 31:42.876
Oh, for God's sake, Richard.

31:44.560 --> 31:45.710
Okay.

31:46.600 --> 31:48.034
- Well, you see,
- Yeah.

31:48.040 --> 31:49.554
I don't think you'd ever know
it was a hairpiece.

31:50.200 --> 31:51.679
If you just take a little-- no.

31:52.440 --> 31:54.158
- No-oh-oh.
- What about there?

31:54.160 --> 31:55.958
- No?
- Wouldn't do it there.

31:55.960 --> 31:57.439
- Hey!
- God, no.

31:57.440 --> 31:58.510
Hey, wait a minute.

31:58.520 --> 31:59.715
- It's gotta go.
- What are you--

31:59.720 --> 32:01.154
Come on, man, I need that,
I need that back.

32:01.160 --> 32:03.436
Richard, you're in denial.

32:03.440 --> 32:06.638
It makes you look like
the world's biggest jerk off.

32:06.640 --> 32:08.279
It makes me look like
I've got more hair.

32:08.280 --> 32:09.350
Sit down, Rich--

32:11.320 --> 32:12.834
I need that back.

32:12.840 --> 32:14.035
Fine.

32:14.040 --> 32:16.236
Let me just tell you
how things are, okay, Richard?

32:16.240 --> 32:18.231
You're headin' for egg city.

32:18.240 --> 32:21.597
Located in the chrome dome county
in the state of the cue ball.

32:21.600 --> 32:22.795
Do you understand what
I'm talking about?

32:22.800 --> 32:27.590
In a year, your head will look
like a Christmas tree lot in January.

32:27.600 --> 32:31.435
I understand that.
That's why I need your help.

32:31.440 --> 32:33.113
Have you got some kind
of a thickening agent?

32:33.120 --> 32:35.760
Something I can put in there
and give me a little bit more,

32:35.760 --> 32:37.672
you know, volume, huh?

32:37.680 --> 32:39.592
I can help you, Richard.

32:39.600 --> 32:40.954
How?

32:40.960 --> 32:42.599
Only if you let me.

32:42.600 --> 32:43.875
- Of course.
- Okay.

32:43.880 --> 32:44.916
Now, what I can do--

32:47.600 --> 32:48.920
I can cut your hair.

32:48.920 --> 32:50.877
I can give it shape.

32:50.880 --> 32:53.873
- I can give it style, Richard.
- Come on.

32:53.880 --> 32:56.236
