And Ananias went his way
and entered into the house.

01:03:40.960 --> 01:03:43.600
And laying his hands
on him said,

01:03:43.600 --> 01:03:46.559
"Brother Saul,
the Lord Jesus,

01:03:46.560 --> 01:03:48.870
