01:09:15.520 --> 01:09:16.749
Sure.

01:09:17.880 --> 01:09:19.279
Aren't you gonna open it?

01:09:19.880 --> 01:09:21.678
What am I doin'?

01:09:22.800 --> 01:09:24.996
Okay, let's see.

01:09:28.439 --> 01:09:29.919
