and turned me over
into the hands of the wicked.

01:21:23.760 --> 01:21:25.990
He hath also
taken me by my neck

01:21:26.000 --> 01:21:31.029
<i>and shaken me to pieces
and set me up for his mark.</i>

01:21:31.040 --> 01:21:34.476
<i>His archers compass me
roundabout.</i>

01:21:34.480 --> 01:21:38.599
<i>He cleaveth my reins asunder
and doth not spare.</i>

01:21:38.600 --> 01:21:42.071
<i>He poureth out my gall
upon the ground.</i>

01:21:42.080 --> 01:21:45.471
<i>He breaketh me
with breach upon breach.</i>

01:21:45.480 --> 01:21:48.154
<i>He runneth upon me
like a giant.</i>

01:21:48.160 --> 01:21:51.039
<i>I have sewed sackcloth
upon my skin</i>

